column2: SELECT m.*, p.petromag_g - p.extinction_g as magPetro_g, p.petromag_r - p.extinction_r as magPetro_r, p.petromag_i - p.extinction_i as magPetro_i, p.modelmag_g - p.extinction_g as magModel_g, p.modelmag_r - p.extinction_r as magModel_r, p.modelmag_i - p.extinction_i as magModel_i, p.petromagErr_g, p.petromagErr_r, p.petromagErr_i, p.modelmagErr_g, p.modelmagErr_r, p.modelmagErr_i INTO myDB.lixo_mags FROM PhotoObj as p, myDB.lixo WHERE p.objID = m.objID
